      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, add your <strong>bulgur wheat</strong> to a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> (the same as you would for pasta)</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 7-9 min or until tender with a slight bite</p>",
