    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>sourdough pitta[s]</strong> to a<strong> toaster</strong> for 1-2 min or until warmed through</p><p>Once the chicken is cooked through, remove the pan from the heat and add your<strong> harissa paste </strong>and a small splash of your <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>(save the rest for later!) with a generous pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>harissa chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
