      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice open the top of the <strong>warmed pitta </strong>and fill it with your <strong>mayo</strong>, an <strong>outer</strong> <strong>lettuce leaf</strong>, a few <strong>tomato slices </strong>and the <strong>harissa chicken</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> tomatoey bulgur</strong> to the side</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the bulgur into a small bowl and turn out</p><p>Serve the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong> with the <strong>remaining white wine vinegar</strong> and a small drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and enjoy!</p>",
